project_descr: This project supports Vanuatu efforts to maintain universal coverage with LLINs for the whole of Vanuatu population at risk.

donor_name: GLOBAL FUND TO FIGHT AIDS, TUBERCULOSIS
outputs.output_descr: The project will play an essential part of the National Malaria Strategic Plan 2015-2020 by procuring and distribute LLINs, provide technical, operational and M&E support to the national Malaria Programme.

project_title: sustaining universal coverage of llins in vanuatu
